## 3. Remaining Gaps

### GAP-03: Notifications Backend Module (Low - Deferred)
- DB table exists but no CRUD API
- Client-side toast notifications work via `notification.store.ts`
- Recommend: Implement as separate feature when needed

### GAP-04: No Tests (Medium - Separate Phase)
- Zero test files
- Recommend: Add in dedicated testing phase

### GAP-07: Dashboard Device/Sensor Summary (Low - UX Enhancement)
- Weather-only dashboard
- Recommend: Add summary cards as UX improvement feature

### GAP-09: User Settings Unused (Low - Deferred)
- Schema exists, no backend implementation
- Recommend: Implement when user preferences feature is needed

